Purpose: Enforce structural, semantic, and governance correctness.
Ross‑OS applies three firewalls:

A. Structural Firewall
Required keys present

Correct data types

No forbidden fields

Violations → REJECTED

B. Semantic Firewall
Regex validation

Enum validation

Required parameter enforcement

Violations → REJECTED

C. Governance Firewall
Action exists in registry

Action is ACTIVE

Action allowed in context

Violations → ESCALATED
